![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/18f5a7cd-9c18-43f6-8e88-41b0cb831a99/341.jpg?format=original)

Grab your Temp V and hold on to your butts as we dive deep into the explosive and chaotic fourth season of _The Boys_. Join us as we dissect every jaw-dropping moment, from the intense showdowns to the shocking betrayals that left us on the edge of our seats. We'll explore the evolution of our favorite characters, the introduction of intriguing new faces, and the social commentary that makes _The Boys_ more than just a superhero show. Did the season live up to its hype? How did it handle the balance between dark humor and serious themes? And what do those cliffhangers mean for the future? Whether you're a die-hard fan or just catching up, this episode is packed with insights you won't want to miss!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

